+/**
+ * Generate Resume Guidance Response (Day 43 Follow-up)
+ *
+ * PURPOSE:
+ * Generates a mock assistant response for resume-related questions.
+ * In production, this would call an AI service.
+ *
+ * WHY THIS EXISTS:
